        <!-- Subtitle -->
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-light-text max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          Start free, upgrade when you need more. No hidden fees, no surprises &mdash; just like a good subscription tracker should be.
